Flask-Sijax Changelog
=====================

Version 0.4.1
-------------

Adds CSRF protection to the examples and docs.

Version 0.4.0
-------------

Adds compatibility with Python 3.


Version 0.3.3
-------------

Fixes a problem with request.files being inaccessible
from upload callbacks when running under Werkzeug 0.9+
("ValueError: I/O operation on closed file").


Version 0.3.0
-------------

The extension now lives in the flask_sijax package,
instead of the flaskext.sijax namespaced package.

Minor backwards incompatible API changes that make Flask-Sijax
more consistent with Flask extension patterns.


Version 0.2.0
-------------

Adds compatibility with Sijax 0.2.0, which introduced some API changes.
The Flask-Sijax API however remains unchanged.


Version 0.1.x
-------------

Initial release.
